    <item>
      <title>罗伯特·肯尼迪 (RFK) Jr. 被任命为卫生与公众服务部部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/rfk-jr-confirmed-as-head-of-health-and-human-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪被任命为美国卫生与公众服务部新任部长，这位曾经的总统候选人公开质疑广泛使用的疫苗的安全性，并承诺从美国食品供应中去除人工食用色素，这标志着美国卫生政策进入新时代。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/rfk-jr-confirmed-as-head-of-health-and-human-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 16:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基告诉特朗普，在和平协议中不能信任普京</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/putin-can-t-be-trusted-in-a-peace-accord-zelenskiy-tells-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统泽连斯基表示，俄罗斯的普京根本不可信，因此乌克兰需要安全保障，尤其是美国的保障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/putin-can-t-be-trusted-in-a-peace-accord-zelenskiy-tells-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 16:06:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于与马斯克和特朗普的关系紧张，SpaceX 南非谈判陷入停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/spacex-s-south-africa-talks-stall-over-musk-trump-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在埃隆·马斯克和他的盟友美国总统唐纳德·特朗普加大公开反对旨在纠正种族隔离造成的种族不平等的法律的力度后，南非与 SpaceX 之间关于推出 Starlink 互联网服务的谈判陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/spacex-s-south-africa-talks-stall-over-musk-trump-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 16:06:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普结束战争的承诺为何让乌克兰感到担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/why-ukraine-is-worried-by-trump-s-promise-to-end-russia-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普长期以来一直表示，他将通过谈判尽快结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/why-ukraine-is-worried-by-trump-s-promise-to-end-russia-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 15:59:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默在简历错误引发争议后支持里夫斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/starmer-backs-reeves-after-controversy-over-incorrect-resume</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 支持财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves)，此前她因其在线简历中的不实信息而面临新的审查，而这一问题已经成为英国财政大臣争议的根源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/starmer-backs-reeves-after-controversy-over-incorrect-resume</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 15:51:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普冻结招聘令野火扑灭者陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-s-hiring-freeze-is-creating-chaos-for-firefighters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着火灾季节即将来临，联邦消防部队面临着不确定性，而洛杉矶的大火却还没有结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-s-hiring-freeze-is-creating-chaos-for-firefighters</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 15:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戴蒙、莫伊尼汉等首席执行官与参议院共和党人就银行去中心化进行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/banking-chiefs-to-talk-debanking-with-senate-banking-committee</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院银行委员会主席蒂姆·斯科特 (Tim Scott) 周四主持了一场与委员会共和党人和银行高管就银行业务去中心化问题的圆桌会议，凸显出华盛顿对这一问题的日益关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/banking-chiefs-to-talk-debanking-with-senate-banking-committee</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 13:54:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将在莫迪访问前宣布全球互惠关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-promises-reciprocal-tariffs-today-without-giving-details</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将于周四宣布实施对等关税的计划，但关税不会立即生效，这是总统针对美国贸易伙伴采取边缘政策的最新例证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-promises-reciprocal-tariffs-today-without-giving-details</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 12:13:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国起诉纽约非法移民身份证法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-sues-new-york-over-state-id-law-for-undocumented-immigrants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的政府正在就 2019 年的一项法律对纽约州提起诉讼，该法律允许无证移民获得州身份证明，同时向联邦当局保密他们的数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/us-sues-new-york-over-state-id-law-for-undocumented-immigrants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 02:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DOGE 削减对最大的政府承包商构成风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/doge-cuts-could-put-largest-government-contractors-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行的分析显示，特朗普政府削减政府支出的举措对整个企业信贷市场的公司构成了短期“低估的风险”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/doge-cuts-could-put-largest-government-contractors-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 21:50:12 GMT</pubDate>
